1
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:21,880
Dad?

2
00:01:22,510 --> 00:01:23,350
Dad?

3
00:01:24,590 --> 00:01:25,430
Dad?

4
00:01:46,540 --> 00:01:50,420
=The Hidden Truth=

5
00:01:50,420 --> 00:01:53,060
=Episode 11=

6
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,200
This new place of mine

7
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:57,070
is way more comfortable than the old one.

8
00:01:59,700 --> 00:02:06,660
(May wealth flow in)

9
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,520
Trust me.

10
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,560
Once we reopen,

11
00:02:11,710 --> 00:02:13,710
you'll be the first call I make.

12
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,360
Of course.

13
00:02:16,910 --> 00:02:17,750
Bye.

14
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,240
Mr. Wang.

15
00:02:23,710 --> 00:02:24,870
Have you made up your mind?

16
00:02:31,030 --> 00:02:32,120
When's the banquet?

17
00:02:33,870 --> 00:02:34,710
Where?

18
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,120
I don't know yet.

19
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:40,630
Bai's still preparing.

20
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,960
I'm waiting for his word.

21
00:02:43,470 --> 00:02:44,360
But right now,

22
00:02:45,710 --> 00:02:47,360
the question is you.

23
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,710
What's your decision?

24
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:55,400
Don't stress too much.

25
00:02:55,870 --> 00:02:57,960
I can bring my guys to back you up.

26
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,030
But like I said,

27
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,840
I won't do the killing for you.

28
00:03:11,630 --> 00:03:12,470
This time,

29
00:03:15,310 --> 00:03:16,430
I will cook myself.

30
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,400
What did you buy?

31
00:03:49,190 --> 00:03:50,240
Buy one, get one free.

32
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:51,190
That's solid.

33
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:55,310
Hello? Anyone?

34
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:58,840
Neighbors?

35
00:04:00,170 --> 00:04:01,120
- Yeah.
- That's right.

36
00:04:01,130 --> 00:04:02,080
Could you help me

37
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,750
call a locksmith?

38
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,560
Dad?

39
00:04:18,950 --> 00:04:19,790
Dad?

40
00:04:31,950 --> 00:04:32,790
Yimo,

41
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,480
where are you going?

42
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,440
Out for a bit.

43
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,600
Let me go with you.

44
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:47,960
Ms. Tong,

45
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,560
let's talk inside.

46
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:50,760
Okay.

47
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,200
Yimo,

48
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:05,040
listen to me.

49
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,560
Ms. Tong,

50
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,720
about what happened before,

51
00:05:09,870 --> 00:05:11,240
my dad chose to let it go

52
00:05:11,430 --> 00:05:12,950
because he had feelings for you.

53
00:05:14,390 --> 00:05:15,560
So I didn't say much.

54
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:17,630
I only hope

55
00:05:18,510 --> 00:05:20,070
that once it settles,

56
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,830
you and my dad can live a good life.

57
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,200
Yimo,

58
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,360
what are you going to do?

59
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:30,040
You don't need to know.

60
00:05:30,630 --> 00:05:31,680
Just watch my dad for me.

61
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,120
Don't let him be reckless.

62
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:34,840
No.

63
00:05:35,630 --> 00:05:36,600
I can't let you leave.

64
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,200
Ms. Tong.

65
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:45,880
Listen to me.

66
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,440
Mr. Bai,

67
00:08:10,070 --> 00:08:12,600
you've been looking for me?

68
00:08:15,310 --> 00:08:16,150
Sit.

69
00:08:17,570 --> 00:08:18,640
I've been waiting for you.

70
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,000
Looks familiar?

71
00:09:07,150 --> 00:09:09,000
Having a meal with you

72
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,550
wasn't easy.

73
00:09:26,390 --> 00:09:27,230
Let's eat.

74
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,080
Why aren't you eating?

75
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:56,480
Not to your taste?

76
00:10:08,270 --> 00:10:09,110
I'm picky.

77
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:11,800
This meal...

78
00:10:12,510 --> 00:10:15,240
You should enjoy it by yourself.

79
00:10:16,030 --> 00:10:16,870
After all,

80
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,510
there won't be many chances

81
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,280
like this again.

82
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,040
Yimo?

83
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,440
Yimo?

84
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:08,710
Wang Yimo?

85
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,200
Ali.

86
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,510
She left.

87
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:14,320
How could you

88
00:11:14,550 --> 00:11:16,670
lock your daughter inside

89
00:11:16,670 --> 00:11:17,750
before leaving?

90
00:11:17,750 --> 00:11:18,870
She called a locksmith.

91
00:11:18,870 --> 00:11:20,550
Here. Your new keys.

92
00:11:21,630 --> 00:11:22,470
Thanks.

93
00:11:22,550 --> 00:11:23,390
No problem.

94
00:11:47,620 --> 00:11:50,020
(Li Tong)

95
00:11:50,750 --> 00:11:51,590
Hello?

96
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:52,750
Ali.

97
00:11:53,290 --> 00:11:54,130
Yimo came back

98
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:55,240
and ran out again.

99
00:11:55,420 --> 00:11:56,270
I tried to stop her.

100
00:11:56,270 --> 00:11:57,360
But I couldn't.

101
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,200
Hello, Bai.

102
00:12:32,030 --> 00:12:32,870
I know it's you.

103
00:12:33,910 --> 00:12:34,910
Let my daughter go.

104
00:12:35,510 --> 00:12:36,790
This has nothing to do with her.

105
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:38,670
Nothing to do with her?

106
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:41,320
How could it not?

107
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:44,320
Everything is about her.

108
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:46,440
If it weren't for her,

109
00:12:47,030 --> 00:12:48,270
we wouldn't be like this.

110
00:12:48,750 --> 00:12:49,790
Bai, listen to me.

111
00:12:51,150 --> 00:12:52,360
Come at me.

112
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:54,270
Don't touch my daughter.

113
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,270
Your daughter?

114
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:04,390
Your daughter's been dead for years.

115
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:06,960
All these years,

116
00:13:07,030 --> 00:13:09,000
you found yourself a stand-in.

117
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,360
Raised her like she was your own.

118
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:11,630
Wang Li,

119
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:16,240
so the little Huahua
who almost got me killed back then

120
00:13:16,510 --> 00:13:17,550
was in your hands.

121
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,040
No.

122
00:13:20,910 --> 00:13:21,910
She's in my hands.

123
00:13:22,590 --> 00:13:23,850
The afternoon after tomorrow.

124
00:13:24,020 --> 00:13:25,360
The cement plant outside the city.

125
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:26,910
Come alone.

126
00:13:31,030 --> 00:13:31,870
Ali,

127
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:32,910
I'll go with you.

128
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,240
I'm going alone.

129
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:36,550
Otherwise,

130
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:38,390
my daughter's in danger.

131
00:13:42,180 --> 00:13:44,060
(Procaine Injection)

132
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,840
This little girl

133
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,270
is pretty tough.

134
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,080
Just like her dad.

135
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:17,680
Master.

136
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,160
Got it.

137
00:14:24,870 --> 00:14:26,670
Huangshan toll station

138
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:28,000
caught Wang Li's car on camera.

139
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:30,670
The first time was at 11:41.

140
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:33,030
And the second time

141
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:35,200
was at 1:26.

142
00:14:35,870 --> 00:14:38,030
That's about an hour and a half.

143
00:14:38,870 --> 00:14:40,750
Plenty of time

144
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,270
to dig up a body in the hills

145
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:43,870
and dump it by the road.

146
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,080
It must be him.

147
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:50,510
Wang Li dug up the remains

148
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:53,320
has to be tied to the Naked Banquet Case.

149
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:55,790
He's the missing piece

150
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,600
from fifteen years ago.

151
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:00,320
The kitchen team at the banquet

152
00:15:01,390 --> 00:15:02,440
must've been his people.

153
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:06,200
Have forensics

154
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:07,440
push harder.

155
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:08,840
See if we can find

156
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:10,440
any direct evidence.

157
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:22,080
Something's off.

158
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:23,680
Really off.

159
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:25,790
I've got a bad feeling.

160
00:15:27,510 --> 00:15:28,440
Maybe we shouldn't wait.

161
00:15:28,670 --> 00:15:29,790
Bring him in now.

162
00:15:31,150 --> 00:15:32,960
You think

163
00:15:33,150 --> 00:15:34,000
he dug up the body

164
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:36,080
to draw our attention

165
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:37,680
to Bai?

166
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:38,960
Exactly.

167
00:15:40,910 --> 00:15:42,440
You and I both know Wang Li.

168
00:15:43,150 --> 00:15:44,320
He's sharp,

169
00:15:45,270 --> 00:15:46,820
and he knows how to cover his tracks.

170
00:15:47,390 --> 00:15:49,480
This move's too abnormal.

171
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:52,910
The reason you're uneasy

172
00:15:53,750 --> 00:15:54,590
is probably

173
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:56,200
connected to Wang Yimo.

174
00:16:00,270 --> 00:16:01,670
I tried calling her

175
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:05,080
to ask about Wang Li.

176
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:06,920
No answer.

177
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,670
Something's happened to them.

178
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:15,960
Go get Wang Li.

179
00:16:16,040 --> 00:16:17,160
Use Zhang Ming as the excuse.

180
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:18,280
Bring him in quietly.

181
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:20,120
Don't tip him off.

182
00:16:20,910 --> 00:16:21,960
See how he reacts.

183
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:25,680
Yes, sir.

184
00:17:45,610 --> 00:17:47,070
I just need to ask you a few things.

185
00:17:47,070 --> 00:17:48,000
Don't run.

186
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:50,070
Wang Yimo's been abducted.

187
00:17:50,550 --> 00:17:51,440
I have to save her.

188
00:17:51,790 --> 00:17:52,660
Where?

189
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:54,030
I'll call the team. Don't go alone.

190
00:17:55,310 --> 00:17:56,150
Right now,

191
00:17:57,030 --> 00:17:58,640
you're the only one I trust.

192
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:00,590
Open the door.

193
00:18:00,590 --> 00:18:01,790
I'm coming with you.

194
00:18:02,070 --> 00:18:03,480
I have to go alone now.

195
00:18:04,350 --> 00:18:05,190
Before three.

196
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,310
At the cement plant.

197
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:09,550
If anything happens to me,

198
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:11,510
take care of Yimo.

199
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:14,840
Wang Li!

200
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:29,830
Master, Wang Yimo was abducted.

201
00:18:29,830 --> 00:18:30,790
Wang Li went on his own.

202
00:18:31,310 --> 00:18:32,200
I couldn't stop him.

203
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:33,310
Three p.m. The cement plant.

204
00:18:33,310 --> 00:18:34,640
Bring backup. I'm going now.

205
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:50,000
Bai?

206
00:18:54,310 --> 00:18:55,150
Bai?

207
00:19:05,310 --> 00:19:06,150
Bai?

208
00:19:06,790 --> 00:19:07,720
Bai?

209
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:09,320
Where are you?

210
00:19:17,590 --> 00:19:18,430
Yimo?

211
00:19:19,030 --> 00:19:20,510
Wang Yimo!

212
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:34,070
How do I get up there?

213
00:19:34,310 --> 00:19:35,480
Bai, come out!

214
00:19:36,240 --> 00:19:37,080
Bai!

215
00:19:38,440 --> 00:19:39,440
Bai!

216
00:19:40,880 --> 00:19:41,790
Mr. Wang.

217
00:19:47,270 --> 00:19:48,110
Li Xu,

218
00:19:49,160 --> 00:19:50,160
you prick.

219
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:51,170
Pocketed it and bailed?

220
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:53,400
I found Bai for you.

221
00:19:53,750 --> 00:19:54,880
He's right here.

222
00:19:55,550 --> 00:19:56,750
You said

223
00:19:57,070 --> 00:19:58,200
you'd handle it yourself.

224
00:19:58,240 --> 00:19:59,310
I didn't stop you, did I?

225
00:19:59,790 --> 00:20:01,550
Our deal is over.

226
00:20:02,550 --> 00:20:03,510
What do you mean?

227
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:05,160
I had a deal with you.

228
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:07,270
I had one with him too.

229
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:10,440
Now it's between me and Bai.

230
00:20:12,070 --> 00:20:12,910
Go.

231
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:23,840
Li Xu.

232
00:20:24,790 --> 00:20:26,160
You scumbag!

233
00:20:27,830 --> 00:20:28,670
Let me go!

234
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:30,590
Stop!

235
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:40,840
Get him!

236
00:20:58,110 --> 00:20:58,950
Darn it!

237
00:21:06,440 --> 00:21:07,280
Freeze!

238
00:21:12,110 --> 00:21:12,950
Police!

239
00:21:14,790 --> 00:21:15,880
Drop it! Don't move!

240
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:17,320
Police! Don't move!

241
00:21:17,590 --> 00:21:19,200
- Don't move.
- Drop it! Now!

242
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:24,320
Captain Zhao.

243
00:21:24,470 --> 00:21:25,320
Captain Zhao.

244
00:21:25,440 --> 00:21:26,480
Save my daughter.

245
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:28,840
Where is she?

246
00:21:30,110 --> 00:21:31,200
She's up there.

247
00:21:33,030 --> 00:21:33,870
Where is she?

248
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,240
Where's Tang Tang?

249
00:21:35,480 --> 00:21:36,320
Tang Tang?

250
00:21:37,110 --> 00:21:38,270
He went that way.

251
00:22:13,560 --> 00:22:14,700
Tang Tang!

252
00:22:23,070 --> 00:22:23,910
Tang Tang.

253
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,080
Tang Tang.

254
00:22:29,270 --> 00:22:31,310
Ambulance!

255
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:49,480
Mrs. Tang.

256
00:22:50,110 --> 00:22:50,950
Mrs. Tang.

257
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:52,350
Tang.

258
00:23:37,380 --> 00:23:40,020
(Operating Room)

259
00:23:52,350 --> 00:23:53,790
Doctor, is he okay?

260
00:23:54,720 --> 00:23:55,810
He's not seriously injured.

261
00:23:55,880 --> 00:23:56,750
After treatment,

262
00:23:56,830 --> 00:23:58,310
his vitals are stable.

263
00:24:02,540 --> 00:24:07,260
(Operating Room)

264
00:24:34,750 --> 00:24:37,030
What's wrong with you?

265
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:39,750
What do you think?

266
00:24:40,310 --> 00:24:42,440
Who knew Wang Li would call the cops?

267
00:24:53,750 --> 00:24:54,920
Contact the company.

268
00:24:55,790 --> 00:24:57,110
Have them figure something out.

269
00:24:58,200 --> 00:25:00,480
We need to leave now.

270
00:25:03,750 --> 00:25:05,750
Stop it. I can't read that.

271
00:25:10,580 --> 00:25:12,940
(You've lost control. Company spoiled you.)

272
00:25:17,790 --> 00:25:18,750
Lost control?

273
00:25:19,830 --> 00:25:20,670
Tell me.

274
00:25:21,280 --> 00:25:22,270
How did I lose control?

275
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:24,030
Where?

276
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:30,080
Caicai.

277
00:25:30,480 --> 00:25:32,030
You dare to push me this far?

278
00:25:33,440 --> 00:25:34,720
Listen to me carefully.

279
00:25:34,830 --> 00:25:35,670
Right now,

280
00:25:36,960 --> 00:25:38,830
we're in the same boat.

281
00:25:40,310 --> 00:25:41,720
If you want to walk away clean,

282
00:25:42,310 --> 00:25:43,400
you'll have to protect me.

283
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,030
Either we leave together,

284
00:25:46,160 --> 00:25:47,000
or

285
00:25:47,920 --> 00:25:48,760
we die together.

286
00:25:49,440 --> 00:25:50,280
Got it?

287
00:26:05,400 --> 00:26:06,240
Master.

288
00:26:10,830 --> 00:26:11,670
How are you feeling?

289
00:26:13,510 --> 00:26:14,350
Thirsty.

290
00:26:15,110 --> 00:26:15,950
Alright.

291
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:24,000
No, wait.

292
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:24,840
Hold on.

293
00:26:30,270 --> 00:26:31,110
Slow down.

294
00:26:39,480 --> 00:26:40,550
Did we get everyone?

295
00:26:41,400 --> 00:26:43,000
Only Wang Li and Li Xu's men.

296
00:26:43,510 --> 00:26:44,350
We couldn't find

297
00:26:45,110 --> 00:26:45,950
Wang Yimo.

298
00:26:47,070 --> 00:26:48,270
She must've taken

299
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:49,240
before we arrived.

300
00:26:59,160 --> 00:27:01,480
Need some vitamin?

301
00:27:02,110 --> 00:27:04,030
I just peeled an apple.

302
00:27:04,550 --> 00:27:05,390
Well...

303
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:10,800
Alright.

304
00:27:10,830 --> 00:27:11,670
Alright, alright.

305
00:27:12,640 --> 00:27:13,960
Easy. Don't laugh.

306
00:27:18,310 --> 00:27:19,350
Be careful.

307
00:27:19,510 --> 00:27:20,350
Okay.

308
00:27:22,110 --> 00:27:23,400
I'm fine. Really.

309
00:27:24,270 --> 00:27:25,270
Be careful.

310
00:27:25,270 --> 00:27:26,110
Watch the steps.

311
00:27:27,480 --> 00:27:28,680
We're home.

312
00:27:32,510 --> 00:27:33,370
Easy, easy.

313
00:27:33,400 --> 00:27:34,350
It's alright.

314
00:27:37,680 --> 00:27:39,030
I'll sit for a bit.

315
00:27:39,030 --> 00:27:40,200
Get some rest.

316
00:27:48,030 --> 00:27:48,870
Careful, it's hot.

317
00:27:50,030 --> 00:27:50,870
Master.

318
00:27:51,320 --> 00:27:52,210
Don't do this.

319
00:27:52,240 --> 00:27:53,270
You're making me nervous.

320
00:27:54,030 --> 00:27:55,000
How come?

321
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:57,310
I'm just being nice.

322
00:28:00,550 --> 00:28:01,880
Sorry, old man.

323
00:28:02,510 --> 00:28:04,000
Been a rough few days for you.

324
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:05,880
I've made you worry and scared.

325
00:28:06,680 --> 00:28:07,830
You've got thick skin

326
00:28:07,830 --> 00:28:09,000
and you're still saying sorry?

327
00:28:11,110 --> 00:28:12,550
Lucky, though.

328
00:28:13,240 --> 00:28:14,640
You fell from that height

329
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:16,160
and barely hurt.

330
00:28:18,180 --> 00:28:20,310
Maybe your parents

331
00:28:21,510 --> 00:28:22,440
are watching over you.

332
00:28:28,200 --> 00:28:29,040
You know,

333
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:31,830
waiting outside the OR for you,

334
00:28:32,160 --> 00:28:33,070
this old heart of mine

335
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:34,920
almost gave out from the fear.

336
00:28:35,590 --> 00:28:37,480
Only happened twice in my life.

337
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:38,920
Last time was your parents.

338
00:28:48,100 --> 00:28:48,960
Sit. Sit.

339
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:49,820
Don't stand.

340
00:28:49,830 --> 00:28:51,030
Making me nervous.

341
00:29:01,310 --> 00:29:02,150
Old man,

342
00:29:04,240 --> 00:29:05,080
you have

343
00:29:06,680 --> 00:29:08,000
never told me

344
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:09,350
how my parents died.

345
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:12,310
Can you tell me today?

346
00:29:24,270 --> 00:29:25,110
Back then,

347
00:29:27,030 --> 00:29:28,110
your parents and I

348
00:29:28,110 --> 00:29:29,790
were working

349
00:29:30,830 --> 00:29:32,960
a wildlife smuggling case.

350
00:29:33,880 --> 00:29:34,880
During the chase,

351
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:36,840
I was driving,

352
00:29:37,750 --> 00:29:39,070
and the criminals rammed us.

353
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:41,240
Your parents died

354
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:43,760
in the crash.

355
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:53,920
After that,

356
00:29:54,750 --> 00:29:55,960
I couldn't drive anymore.

357
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:05,310
Bai Qiming

358
00:30:06,160 --> 00:30:07,590
was in that ring too.

359
00:30:08,480 --> 00:30:09,590
He was a minor player.

360
00:30:10,440 --> 00:30:12,200
We had no direct evidence.

361
00:30:13,400 --> 00:30:14,510
He got away.

362
00:30:15,400 --> 00:30:16,830
Bai Qiming?

363
00:30:20,240 --> 00:30:22,920
I never thought he'd be tied to that case.

364
00:30:23,510 --> 00:30:25,310
Seeing him again
in the Naked Banquet Case,

365
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:27,640
I regretted it deeply.

366
00:30:28,440 --> 00:30:30,240
If we'd widened the net

367
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,090
back then,

368
00:30:31,110 --> 00:30:32,480
maybe none of that

369
00:30:32,750 --> 00:30:33,720
would've happened.

370
00:30:34,350 --> 00:30:35,190
I really...

371
00:30:36,510 --> 00:30:39,030
I really regret it.

372
00:30:40,510 --> 00:30:41,790
That's enough.

373
00:30:42,200 --> 00:30:43,590
What do you always teach me?

374
00:30:45,160 --> 00:30:46,110
Anyway,

375
00:30:46,260 --> 00:30:47,880
cases are cases.

376
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:50,030
Facts matter.

377
00:30:50,550 --> 00:30:53,070
Criminals were too cunning.

378
00:30:53,440 --> 00:30:54,750
That's not on you.

379
00:30:56,310 --> 00:30:57,240
Look at me.

380
00:30:57,960 --> 00:30:59,110
I became a detective

381
00:30:59,110 --> 00:31:00,030
and a pretty good one.

382
00:31:00,590 --> 00:31:02,200
I do this not just for my parents,

383
00:31:04,270 --> 00:31:05,350
but for you too.

384
00:31:08,960 --> 00:31:10,030
What's hanging there?

385
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:11,590
Certificate of Honor.

386
00:31:11,790 --> 00:31:13,030
(Certificate of Honor)
Comrade Zhao Fengcheng.

387
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:14,440
Third-Class Merit.

388
00:31:16,310 --> 00:31:17,720
You're a good cop.

389
00:31:20,720 --> 00:31:21,560
Right.

390
00:31:25,540 --> 00:31:29,660
(For Outstanding Service;
Zhao Fengcheng; Third-Class Merit)

391
00:31:55,200 --> 00:31:56,880
Time to get up. What time is it?

392
00:31:57,750 --> 00:31:59,920
Recovering doesn't mean sleeping all day.

393
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:02,550
Let me sleep a bit more, just a little.

394
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:05,280
What do you want for breakfast?

395
00:32:05,480 --> 00:32:07,640
Wontons or Soup Dumplings.

396
00:32:07,750 --> 00:32:08,590
Alright.

397
00:32:10,190 --> 00:32:11,370
There's an apple on the table.

398
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:12,280
Eat it

399
00:32:12,440 --> 00:32:13,480
before it browns.

400
00:32:14,790 --> 00:32:16,240
Perfectly peeled today.

401
00:32:17,510 --> 00:32:19,400
Thank you.

402
00:32:26,830 --> 00:32:27,670
Zhao.

403
00:32:27,920 --> 00:32:28,790
Paid already.

404
00:32:28,790 --> 00:32:29,640
Okay.

405
00:32:31,510 --> 00:32:32,590
How's Tang Tang?

406
00:32:32,590 --> 00:32:33,490
He's fine.

407
00:32:33,510 --> 00:32:34,350
Good.

408
00:32:34,480 --> 00:32:36,160
- See you.
- Yeah, see you.

409
00:32:46,310 --> 00:32:47,480
Robbery!

410
00:32:47,640 --> 00:32:49,030
Give me my bag!

411
00:32:49,590 --> 00:32:50,590
Help!

412
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:52,240
Anyone?

413
00:33:51,070 --> 00:33:52,480
- Hello, 911?
- Call the police!

414
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:53,790
Someone's stabbed!

415
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:24,760
♪Dreams of the past sleep in the chill♪

416
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:28,200
♪Now I run toward the light♪

417
00:34:30,040 --> 00:34:35,320
♪What does the fire burn,
what does it reveal?♪

418
00:34:35,640 --> 00:34:39,280
♪Is the answer found when the sun rises♪

419
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:44,200
♪If it's all a lie♪

420
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:49,560
♪Should I tear it open?♪

421
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:55,600
♪If it's all part of the journey♪

422
00:34:56,280 --> 00:35:01,120
♪Then face the blaze head-on♪

423
00:35:01,520 --> 00:35:06,000
♪Let the sun awaken my heart's crave♪

424
00:35:06,520 --> 00:35:12,240
♪Pain reminds me I'm alive♪

425
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:17,200
♪The world can't take away every clear sky♪

426
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:23,000
♪The hotter it gets, the fiercer I fight♪

427
00:35:23,280 --> 00:35:28,000
♪Let the sun burn away all I lean upon♪

428
00:35:28,360 --> 00:35:34,000
♪Leave me only what endures♪

429
00:35:34,120 --> 00:35:39,680
♪At the cliff's edge, all fear shatters♪

430
00:35:39,720 --> 00:35:46,680
♪With a grounded heart, a soul like fire♪
